# iGopherHD

Native iOS application developed using Objective-C, designed as an early-stage mobile product focusing on performance and user interaction.

## 📱 Overview

iGopherHD is a native iOS application created during the early stages of mobile development adoption.  
The project demonstrates experience in building structured iOS applications, handling UI layouts, and managing application lifecycle.

## 🚀 Features

- Native iOS application (Objective-C)  
- Custom UI layouts for iPhone and iPad  
- Responsive interface for different screen orientations  
- Application lifecycle and state management  

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Objective-C  
- iOS SDK  
- Xcode  

## 📱 Platform

- iOS (iPhone & iPad support)

## 👨‍💻 Role

Full-cycle development:
- Application architecture  
- UI implementation  
- Core logic development  
- Testing and optimization  

## 📅 Note

This project represents an early phase of my career in mobile development and reflects over a decade of hands-on experience in building iOS applications.

